msg: * lib/elementtree-1.2.6-20050316.tar.gz, lib/elementtree-1.2.6-20050316: import the 20050316 release of the ElementTree package, which is a dependency for the Kid template language. See http://effbot.org/ for details. ElementTree is licensed under an MIT-style license.

author: leosimons
msg: * lib/kid-0.8.tar.gz, lib/kid-0.8: import the 0.8 release of the Kid template language implementation. See http://kid.lesscode.org/ for details. Kid is licensed under the MIT license.

author: akarasulu
msg: Setting up for multiproject configuration with subprojects for:
